channel.title: [Delta] Pk-Ops Server+Client Source Release [Delta] First Source
channel.description:
Well, this is my server Its pretty cool for beginners Enjoy :D
Source - [url=http://www.mediafire.com/?uupuxnx5z58fwzn]http://www.mediafire.com/?uupuxnx5z58fwzn[/url]
Client - [url=http://www.mediafire.com/?voubnxr9py77r9m]http://www.mediafire.com/?voubnxr9py77r9m[/url]
~Features~ Dungeoneering Minigame (Lol, well maybe killing monsters for tokens minigame :D) D claws spec and emote :) Lil Bit of custom items (easily removeable) Mining & Smithing Dueling( Right click on a player anywhere and select DUEL) Thats it really -- You can add much more stuff and make this source pretty awesome --
Pictures
[IMG]http://i522.photobucket.com/albums/w344/himenub/pkops.png[/img] [IMG]http://i522.photobucket.com/albums/w344/himenub/pkopsstarter.png[/img] [IMG]http://i522.photobucket.com/albums/w344/himenub/homepk.png[/img] [IMG]http://i522.photobucket.com/albums/w344/himenub/pkopspnts.png[/img] [IMG]http://i522.photobucket.com/albums/w344/himenub/thieveingpkops.png[/img] [IMG]http://i522.photobucket.com/albums/w344/himenub/pkshop.png[/img] [IMG]http://i522.photobucket.com/albums/w344/himenub/miningnsmithin.png[/img] [IMG]http://i522.photobucket.com/albums/w344/himenub/dungminiplaceee.png[/img] [IMG]http://i522.photobucket.com/albums/w344/himenub/dungminirewards.png[/img] [IMG]http://i522.photobucket.com/albums/w344/himenub/dclawsperfspec.png[/img] [IMG]http://i522.photobucket.com/albums/w344/himenub/donarzonecontru.png[/img] [IMG]http://i522.photobucket.com/albums/w344/himenub/enjoysmiley.png[/img]
Credits 20% Me - Changing stuff and adding a cute minigame XD and other stuff 80% Evolution X- Providing most things.
By Dharmesh Enjoy :)
